    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little sad to part with this beauty, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve seriously babied it since day one! It still has that fresh feel and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dings, just a super smooth ride that's been kept spotless. If you're looking for a total gem that\u2019s been loved and cared for, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
